1
00:00:11,636 --> 00:00:13,471
I like you, teacher.

2
00:00:15,098 --> 00:00:17,183
You did well on this.

3
00:00:21,229 --> 00:00:22,605
Please grant me one wish.

4
00:00:23,815 --> 00:00:26,067
A wish?

5
00:00:26,067 --> 00:00:27,902
Did we ever make that kind of promise?

6
00:00:30,113 --> 00:00:31,948
Am I not pretty?

7
00:00:34,826 --> 00:00:37,203
What should I do...

8
00:00:37,203 --> 00:00:40,206
I like smart people.

9
00:00:40,915 --> 00:00:44,836
With these grades, you wouldn’t even get near our school.

10
00:00:54,721 --> 00:00:55,847
Ah.

11
00:00:56,681 --> 00:00:58,808
I really like you, teacher.

12
00:00:58,808 --> 00:01:00,602
You even show up

13
00:01:00,602 --> 00:01:02,020
in my dreams.

14
00:01:07,901 --> 00:01:09,986
Geez.

15
00:01:09,986 --> 00:01:11,404
You’re such a kid.

16
00:01:26,211 --> 00:01:27,545
Why isn’t Jeong-yeon here?

17
00:01:37,722 --> 00:01:40,517
Is he sick or something?

18
00:01:51,778 --> 00:01:53,363
Sorry I’m late.

19
00:01:56,658 --> 00:01:59,452
Whoa—did you get into a fight?

20
00:01:59,452 --> 00:02:01,746
Do you need a lawyer? I know someone.

21
00:02:01,996 --> 00:02:06,543
No, it’s nothing. I’m fine.

22
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,878
If it’s nothing serious,

23
00:02:08,878 --> 00:02:11,047
let’s start the experiment for HQ first.

24
00:02:11,798 --> 00:02:14,300
Wow, that’s cold.

25
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,927
Are you insane about work?

26
00:02:15,927 --> 00:02:17,053
Hey.

27
00:02:17,053 --> 00:02:18,847
Do you get paid more than me?

28
00:02:18,847 --> 00:02:20,181
What are you talking about?

29
00:02:24,602 --> 00:02:27,480
Jeong-yeon.

30
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,773
Come over here.

31
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,695
I’ll skip the explanation.

32
00:03:57,695 --> 00:04:01,532
This is Case Delphi, trial six.

33
00:04:01,532 --> 00:04:05,286
What’s the most precious memory of your life?

34
00:04:06,079 --> 00:04:07,622
Um...

35
00:04:07,622 --> 00:04:11,042
I used to spend a lot of time with my first love.

36
00:04:11,042 --> 00:04:15,296
Every single day back then was precious to me.

37
00:04:16,381 --> 00:04:18,758
And the worst memory?

38
00:04:20,802 --> 00:04:24,430
I confessed, we even kissed.

39
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:28,601
And then he patted my head

40
00:04:28,601 --> 00:04:31,562
and said it was “just a momentary feeling.”

41
00:04:31,562 --> 00:04:33,731
Wow. What a jerk.

42
00:04:34,357 --> 00:04:38,069
Right? Pretty awful.

43
00:04:38,778 --> 00:04:40,071
Jeong-yeon.

44
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:46,119
Shall we step outside and talk?

45
00:05:11,769 --> 00:05:15,064
Are you rebelling again, now of all times?

46
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,986
Oh, this?

47
00:05:24,991 --> 00:05:28,286
I thought you might care if I looked beaten up.
Like before.

48
00:05:33,249 --> 00:05:34,834
Then what about your hand?

49
00:05:45,303 --> 00:05:47,889
You’re still a kid.

50
00:05:49,474 --> 00:05:52,435
I’m grown up now, you know?

51
00:05:52,435 --> 00:05:56,147
You don’t need to feel guilty anymore.

52
00:05:56,147 --> 00:05:58,733
If you want to sleep with me, you can.

53
00:05:59,734 --> 00:06:01,819
You’ve got some nerve for someone so small.

54
00:06:04,072 --> 00:06:06,491
Ha.

55
00:06:07,241 --> 00:06:10,328
You’re not my type.

56
00:06:10,328 --> 00:06:12,872
Yeah, right.

57
00:06:15,917 --> 00:06:17,627
Why do you think that?

58
00:06:19,003 --> 00:06:22,090
You like pretty types like me.

59
00:06:23,925 --> 00:06:25,301
I saw everything.

60
00:06:29,055 --> 00:06:30,348
Saw what?

61
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:37,980
My observation notes from high school.

62
00:07:07,218 --> 00:07:11,305
[Emotional Attachment Formation
and Correction Experiment
in At-Risk Adolescents]

63
00:07:39,292 --> 00:07:44,130
(It was all written there. About me.)

64
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:47,550
(He shows a strong interest in appearance.)

65
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:52,138
(Especially when called “pretty,”
he blushes.)

66
00:07:52,138 --> 00:07:54,474
(Jeong-yeon is pretty.)

67
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:07,570
Back then, you were young.

68
00:08:07,570 --> 00:08:10,406
You were perfect as an experiment subject.

69
00:08:13,701 --> 00:08:17,830
Was that really all it was?

70
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:20,583
And...

71
00:08:22,543 --> 00:08:25,838
Just...

72
00:08:25,838 --> 00:08:28,966
a cute student.
